Site Update Instructions:

Adding/Removing Sites
----------------------
Step 1: Open index.html and click the pencil in the top right to edit the file. 

Step 2: Scroll to line 572 and you will see the site registry list.

At the bottom of the list, type in the new site, matching the formatting of the site above.

For example, I'm adding Bonnieville KY here:

    stAnnMO:           {name:"St. Ann, MO", lat:38.727, lon:-90.385},
    stPetersburgFL:    {name:"St. Petersburg, FL", lat:27.767, lon:-82.640},
    vancouverWA:       {name:"Vancouver, WA", lat:45.6366, lon:-122.6615},
    westColumbiaSC:    {name:"West Columbia, SC", lat:33.994, lon:-81.074},
    zanesvilleOH:      {name:"Zanesville, OH", lat:39.9403, lon:-82.0132},
    bonnievilleKY:     {name:"Bonnieville, KY"},
};

NOTE: Latitude and Longitude numbers are not needed for new sites. 

From there you can add them to a category. 


Adding/Removing Categories
---------------------------

This is a similar process to adding sites

At line 537, you will see the category block.

You add a new line, and add the category, the label, then the site ids created in the previous step, again ensuring that the formatting is correct.

In the example below I'm adding a tester site with Bonnieville, KY and West Columbia, SC.

const SITE_CATEGORIES = {
    accountManagement:{label:"Account Management",siteIds:["albanyNY","charlotteNC","cincinnatiOH","coloradoSpringsCO","fondDuLacWI","irvingTX","mcAllenTX","portlandOR","rochesterNY","vancouverWA","zanesvilleOH"]},
    accountManagementChat:{label:"Account Management Chat",siteIds:["elPasoTX","rochesterNY","zanesvilleOH"]},
    crcs:{label:"CRCS",siteIds:["morrisvilleNC"]},
    mobileBilling:{label:"Mobile Billing",siteIds:["albanyNY","mcAllenTX","rochesterNY","vancouverWA"]},
    mobileRepair:{label:"Mobile Repair",siteIds:["amherstNY","clevelandOH","kansasCityMO","mcAllenTX","stPetersburgFL"]},
    repairChat:{label:"Repair Chat",siteIds:["bridgetonMO","elPasoTX","louisvilleKY","morrisvilleNC"]},
    scsEnglishBilling:{label:"SCS English Billing",siteIds:["greensboroNC","sanDiegoCA"]},
    serviceability:{label:"Serviceability",siteIds:["sanAntonioTX","stAnnMO","westColumbiaSC"]},
    smbSpb:{label:"SMB/SPB",siteIds:["charlotteNC","louisvilleKY","austinTX"]},
    technicalSupport:{label:"Technical Support",siteIds:["bridgetonMO","cantonOH","cheektowagaNY","columbusOH","elPasoTX","flushingNY","greensboroNC","louisvilleKY","middletownNY","morrisvilleNC","orlandoFL","sanAntonioTX","stPetersburgFL"]}
    tester:{label:"Testing Sites",siteIds:["bonnievilleKY", "westColumbiaSC"]}
